cadBgpMib.name: cadBgpMib

revisions.description: Removed original tables and add DCL related tables.

cadBgpMib.contactinfo: Customer Support Postal: Arris International Inc. 4343 Commerce Court Lisle, IL 60532 Phone: +1 630 281 3000 Email: support@cadant.com
cadBgpMib.description: The MIB module defined here represent Arris Cadant C4's enterprise specific Border Gateway Protocol MIB.

cadBgpRouteMapAuxTable.name: cadBgpRouteMapAuxTable
cadBgpRouteMapAuxTable.description: This table adds Cadant specific route map parameters.

cadBgpRouteMapAuxEntry.name: cadBgpRouteMapAuxEntry
cadBgpRouteMapAuxEntry.description: An entry that adds Cadant specific route map parameters using the DCL bgpRouteMapTable keys.

cadBgpRouteMapAuxRouteMapName.name: cadBgpRouteMapAuxRouteMapName
cadBgpRouteMapAuxRouteMapName.description: Field containg the name of the Route Map.

cadBgpRouteMapAuxPrefixListName.name: cadBgpRouteMapAuxPrefixListName
cadBgpRouteMapAuxPrefixListName.description: Field containg the name of the Prefix List associated with this Route Map. It is used to match on cadPolicyPfxListName.

cadBgpRouteMapAuxPreMatch.name: cadBgpRouteMapAuxPreMatch
cadBgpRouteMapAuxPreMatch.description: Field indicates which match command is used by the route map the prefix list is tied to.

cadBgpRouteMapAuxMaAddrName.name: cadBgpRouteMapAuxMaAddrName
cadBgpRouteMapAuxMaAddrName.description: Field containg the name of the Prefix List used to match the NLRI attribute against.

cadBgpRouteMapAuxMaNextName.name: cadBgpRouteMapAuxMaNextName
cadBgpRouteMapAuxMaNextName.description: Field containg the name of the Prefix List used to match the Next Hop attribute

cadBgpRouteMapAuxMaSourceName.name: cadBgpRouteMapAuxMaSourceName
cadBgpRouteMapAuxMaSourceName.description: Field containg the name of the Prefix List used to match the source address

cadRtmRedistAuxTable.name: cadRtmRedistAuxTable
cadRtmRedistAuxTable.description: This table adds Cadant redistribution information entries.

cadRtmRedistAuxEntry.name: cadRtmRedistAuxEntry
cadRtmRedistAuxEntry.description: Cadant specific auxiliary information that parallels DC-RTM Redistribution Table

rtmRedistFteIndex.name: rtmRedistFteIndex
rtmRedistFteIndex.description: The HAF entity index identifying the instance of DC-RTM to which this auxiliary table entry applies.

rtmRedistEntryId.name: rtmRedistEntryId
rtmRedistEntryId.description: The index of the parallel DC-RTM redistribution table entry within the DC-RTM entity. This is an arbitrarily selected identifier.

cadRtmRedistAuxRowStatus.name: cadRtmRedistAuxRowStatus
cadRtmRedistAuxRowStatus.description: Used to create and delete a cadRtmRedistAuxTable entry.

cadRtmRedistAuxRouteMapIndex.name: cadRtmRedistAuxRouteMapIndex
cadRtmRedistAuxRouteMapIndex.description: The index of the bgpRouteMapEntry used by this route redistribution.

cadRtmRedistAuxCommandLineMetric.name: cadRtmRedistAuxCommandLineMetric
cadRtmRedistAuxCommandLineMetric.description: Whether of not metric values were set in the command line
